description.narrative: DNDi is headquartered in Geneva, Switzerland, with eight regional offices worldwide located in Cape Town, Kinshasa, Kuala Lumpur, Nairobi, New Delhi, New York, Rio de Janeiro, and Tokyo. DNDi's regional offices house half our staff and are critical to our patient and partnership-driven model, and essential to DNDi’s strategy, identity, and credibility. They oversee clinical trials, support health ministries and national disease control programmes, provide critical links to patients, clinicians, and researchers; and raise funds to make our activities possible.
